Plot: Spicy Tuna is a short comedy about two party girls, Roxy and Lo, on a mission to get their old dance group back together to make quick cash before they're evicted from their New York City apartment.
Title: Spicy Tuna
Writer: Alli Caudle, Alli Caudle (story), Jacquelyn Reyes
Director: Alli Caudle, Josh Mayes, Jacquelyn Reyes, Lauren Richardson, Danny Wantz
Actors: Sophie Sumner, Jacquelyn Reyes, Alli Caudle, Lianna Nielsen
